ACTIVE_ORDERS_TOOLTIP: Total number of active orders in the selected city
AGGRESSION_TOOLTIP_CITY_BASED: Average aggression levels of the warehouses in that city
COMPLIANCE_NA: No planned couriers to calculate compliance
COMPLIANCE_TOOLTIP_CITY_BASED: Percentage of 'Compliant' warehouse count in that city
LATE_TOOLTIP: Total number of late orders in the selected city
LOWER_ETA_TOOLTIP: Average of lower limits of orders containing Estimated Time of Arrival (ETA) interval information
RED_BASKET_TOOLTIP: Total number of red baskets in the selected city
SLOTTED_ORDER_COUNT_SHORT_TOOLTIP: Total number of only scheduled active order count
UPPER_ETA_TOOLTIP: Average of upper limits of orders containing Estimated Time of Arrival (ETA) interval information.
UTILIZATION_TOOLTIP: Percentage of (utilized/utilizable) courier count based on courier status
UTIL_NA: No utilizable couriers to calculate utilization
